
Keep functions under 600 characters... weird <= comments count against char count

--max_inlined_source_size let's you change the size of the functions that can be inlined. Changes the 600 char limit
%SetFlags("--max_inlined_source_size=1000") <-- can be inside node function call

--allow-natives-syntax <-- allows the above stuff to work

